<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.1">
<l>munnīr ñālam paṭaittavem mukilvaṇṇaṉē</l>
<l>yannāṇī tanta vākkaiyiṉ vaḻiyaḻalvēṉ</l>
<l>vennāṇōy vīya viṉaikaḷaivē raṟappāyn</l>
<l>tennāḷyā ṉuṉṉai yiṉivantu kūṭuvēṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O our cloud-coloured one who created the world [surrounded by] the three-watered [sea],</l>
<l>I wander [my] way in the body you gave [me] that day.</l>
<l>Which day shall I now come [and] join you, making a leap</l>
<l>so that karma is cut off an the root, so that the pain of cruel days perishes?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
